c: 3
v: 156
t: "Mwebwe\tmwemeye\tImana\tyanyu\ty’ukuri\tntimube\tnkaba\thakanye Imana\tyabo\ty’ukuri,\tn’ukuvugira hejuru ya bene\twabo\tmugihe\tbagira urugendo rwo ngaha kw’isi canke mugihe batana mumitwe bagapfa, iyo bobaye iwacu ntibari gupfa canke ngo bacikane, kugira ngo Imana ibigire gutyo\tngo\tbibabereko\tagahinda k’umitima yabo, n’Imana niyo irema n’ukwica, n’Imana niyo ibona ibintu vyose mugira"